column2: SELECT TOP # emline.fiberid as fiberID, emline.ra, emline.dec, emline.z as z_noqso, emline.zerr as z_noqso_err, emline.sigmaStars as emline_vdisp, emline.sigmaStarsErr as emline_vdisp_err, sp.veldisp as sp_vdisp, sp.veldisperr as sp_vdisp_err, p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.petroR5#_r, p.fracdeV_r, p.deVRad_r, p.expRad_r, fsps.logMass, fsps.age, fsps.metallicity, s.specobjid, pz.z as photoz FROM emissionLinesPort AS emline, fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) n JOIN specObj as sp ON emline.specobjid = sp.specobjid JOIN PhotoObj AS p on p.objid = n.objid JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = n.objid JOIN PhotoZ AS pz ON pz.objid = n.objid JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as fsps ON s.specobjid = fsps.specobjid WHERE emline.plate = # AND emline.mjd = #
